#: patterns/faq/accordion.php:31
#: patterns/faq/default.php:30
#: patterns/page/home.php:1644
msgid "The framework requires PHP 7.4 as a baseline. For optimal velocity and ecosystem stability, we recommend deploying on PHP 8.3. While the core architecture natively supports up to 8.5, version 8.3 currently offers the safest compatibility balance for third-party extensions."
